OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSpiking crackdown to see   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmore funding for test kits 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, More training for door staff and       
OL,6, funding for testing kits are among a   
OL,7, package of measures announced to crack 
OL,8, down on spiking.                       
OL,10,FThe Home Office has said the law will  
OL,11,Falso be "modernised" to make it clear  
OL,12,Fspiking - putting alcohol or drugs into
OL,13,Fanother person's drink or body without 
OL,14,Ftheir consent - is a crime.            
OL,16,FThe plans have broadly been welcomed by
OL,17,Fcampaigners.                           
OL,19,FBut they stop short of calls from some 
OL,20,Fto make spiking a specific offence.    
